name: TCP Output
xml_template:
<route  id="{{source}}">
    <from uri="direct:{{source}}"/>
    {{#if (eq protocol "mllp")}}
    <to uri="{{protocol}}://{{hostname}}:{{port}}{{path}}{{querystring mllp_query_params}}"/>
    {{/if}}
    {{#if (eq protocol "netty:tcp")}}
    <to uri="{{protocol}}://{{hostname}}:{{port}}{{path}}{{querystring netty_query_params}}"/>
    {{/if}}
</route>
